{"tid":1094284,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"新經理駕到，諗住辭工","createTime":"2019-04-06T07:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T07:51:53.000Z","uid":245803,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0fc9273038b3454e66794f65bb5d83830ef7e85","tid":1094284,"uid":245803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:38:21.000Z","msg":"個經理一泥到唔夠一星期清咗我locker，冇問我係咪唔做。<br />\n好la！其實我有三星期冇返工，因為學校有功課，想大家一齊做好件事，於是返小啲工，想做好份功課！<br />\n之前個經理表示理解，但後來兩星期之後，經理放假，新經理就泥咗！我唔祈求任何人理解我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢可以問下我，wts下都得，佢如果有用，我都可以返去清咗個locker<br />\n同埋個人原因la！呢個時間係我讀書時期，始終都係讀書重要，我想趁讀書做啲野!因為真正出到去做野就好多野要兼顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說呢份工都做咗差唔多兩年，有啲唔捨得，係今年上咗hd，時間難就咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好la 呻下咋 唔留係公司累人累物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce3353aca758aa9ad4112d86a812072c694e187","tid":1094284,"uid":161374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"大學都係前一晚先溫書，hd 就是撚旦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e2b08cfd68418a621045ca11e56d33e0d08e63","tid":1094284,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT